OL,3,CBoy 'hallucinated and clawed his face'
OL,4,Cafter drinking slushy, mother says
OL,6,FThe mother of a little boy is warning
OL,7,Fparents not to let their young
OL,8,Fchildren drink slushies after her four-
OL,9,Fyear-old was rushed to hospital, ITV
OL,10,FNews' Martha Fairlie reports
OL,12,FA mother is calling for more warnings
OL,13,Fagainst slushies after her son started
OL,14,F"clawing at his face, biting himself
OL,15,Fand hallucinating" after drinking one
OL,16,Fat a bowling alley.
