OL,3,CBoy 'hallucinated and clawed his face'
OL,4,Cafter drinking slushy, mother says
OL,6,FThe best-known brand of slushy drink,
OL,7,FSlush Puppie, has said its drinks do
OL,8,Fnot contain glycerol.
OL,10,FThe drinks Professor Robin May from
OL,11,Fthe Food Standards Agency (FSA) said.
OL,13,FHe added that the amount of glycerol
OL,14,Fconsumed should be limited in all
OL,15,Fchildren under 10, as a large quantity
OL,16,Fof the additive can have adverse
OL,17,Feffects in small bodies.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/8
