OL,3,CBoy 'hallucinated and clawed his face'
OL,4,Cafter drinking slushy, mother says
OL,6,F"The issue is if you consume a lot of
OL,7,Fglycerol, fast, particularly if you're
OL,8,Frelatively small ... That can lead
OL,9,Fwater to rush into your blood vessels
OL,10,Fessentially to compensate," he said,
OL,11,Fcomparing the experience to
OL,12,Fdehydration.
OL,14,FChildren's bodies cannot cope with
OL,15,Fglycerol as quickly as normal sugars
OL,16,Fin the blood, and in extreme cases can
OL,17,Fcause shock, low blood sugar and lack
OL,18,Fof consciousness.
