OL,3,CBoy 'hallucinated and clawed his face'
OL,4,Cafter drinking slushy, mother says
OL,6,FMs Green said more obvious guidance is
OL,7,Fneeded to warn parents against the
OL,8,Fside effects of young children
OL,9,Fdrinking slushies.
OL,11,FShe said while there was a sign on the
OL,12,Fopposite side of the bar at the
OL,13,Fbowling alley, the people serving the
OL,14,Fslushies did not ask how old Albie and
OL,15,Fhis friend were.
OL,17,F"There should be checks there should
OL,18,Fbe someone trained to be pouring the
OL,19,Fslushy," she said.
