OL,3,CBoy 'hallucinated and clawed his face'
OL,4,Cafter drinking slushy, mother says
OL,6,F"With the glycerol, especially with
OL,7,Fsugar free slushies they do it based
OL,8,Fon the consistency and to achieve the
OL,9,Fsweetness.
OL,11,F"If you add too much or too little, or
OL,12,Fhowever they mix it on the day just
OL,13,Fdepending on the day, it could have
OL,14,Fresulted in Albie's life being taken,
OL,15,Fwhich was just heartbreaking."
OL,17,FAround 50 million slushy drinks are
OL,18,Fsold in the UK each year, according to
OL,19,Fthe FSA, and there were five cases
OL,20,Fsimilar to Albie's in the last three
OL,21,Fyears.
